><br />\n片幅唔會影響景深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23b7e748e56abc62c416e09057ce8149afd84f4","tid":100921,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T21:44:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96da0fcd2eab3173b079490f8404575ee94c66ef","tid":100921,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你將APSC光圈x1.5大約就係FF個景深<br />\n<br />\nFF有時景深淺影特寫同合照好煩<br />\n借俾外人幫手影更加要收定光圈先，變左有自己入鏡就無淺景深<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n片幅唔會影響景深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n片幅會影響景深</blockquote><br />\n片幅會影響景深<br />\n<br />\n除咗景深之外，仲有可用iso高咗<br />\n買鏡唔使x1.5/1.6<br />\n不過啲gear又重咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832ddb9d52f88ea285dedd8cca0c39357e386f09","tid":100921,"uid":21870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faf3da5e2029bda0e6730617133abf3a3151ebf","tid":100921,"uid":21870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行<span style=\"color: red;\">後咗幾步</span>去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"17e8644b9e741591bd013e0a749820ab3c15b67f","tid":100921,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打唔識唔好扮識wor,景深同pixel density同放大比率都有關係<br />\n<br />\nbtw FF最大優勢係DR大同解放舊鏡,景深呢d野我唔多care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f070caf63a84f452ab38fc81a644731f0b35be","tid":100921,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68fd257d67d8737a6b0918ab52f79d9f19ff108b","tid":100921,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c5999262e1e1d66eb86d9b22ec448d84d0771da","tid":100921,"uid":21870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打唔識唔好扮識wor,景深同pixel density同放大比率都有關係<br />\n<br />\nbtw FF最大優勢係DR大同解放舊鏡,景深呢d野我唔多care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54256f9bbb81aa5b5f15ec66829498d2f207112","tid":100921,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"話影響既係 same frame different Len different distance<br />\n話唔影響既係 same distance same Len different frame<br />\n好似應該咁講"},{"pid":"61165705b5b4703c0fe41b1207884b380670d896","tid":100921,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講無錯，但你影相唔會咁影嘛<br />\n正確黎講係咁<br />\n當apsc同ff都用一個視角影相 (eg 45 度標準人類視角)<br />\nff係淺景深過apsc<br />\n詳情睇下呢條片既中段，雖然係支那片，但幾實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5TwIlzNaco&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fd954916\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco</a>"},{"pid":"0eda450b19605a796bb4dc3a6192de9110025165","tid":100921,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話影響既係 same frame different Len different distance<br />\n話唔影響既係 same distance same Len different frame<br />\n好似應該咁講</blockquote><br />\n不過apsc同ff影相都係用視角黎計，所以話唔影響係呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273d27a9a6c81bc6fcb961e9aa13f0d8d66f92ce","tid":100921,"uid":50056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講無錯，但你影相唔會咁影嘛<br />\n正確黎講係咁<br />\n當apsc同ff都用一個視角影相 (eg 45 度標準人類視角)<br />\nff係淺景深過apsc<br />\n詳情睇下呢條片既中段，雖然係支那片，但幾實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5TwIlzNaco&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fd954916\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco</a></blockquote><br />\n和以前都以為片幅影響景深，點解有呢個講法，只不過係因為要做到相同視角，APSC用23，FF要用35，咁FF張相景深咪淺啲，因為焦距長左。所以影響景深既最後都係得焦距同光圈。"},{"pid":"19ea22195431e79ad65964025afd94c206111416","tid":100921,"uid":50056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc