de crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講無錯，但你影相唔會咁影嘛<br />\n正確黎講係咁<br />\n當apsc同ff都用一個視角影相 (eg 45 度標準人類視角)<br />\nff係淺景深過apsc<br />\n詳情睇下呢條片既中段，雖然係支那片，但幾實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5TwIlzNaco&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fd954916\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco</a></blockquote><br />\n講解得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得係幾好，我唔升ff原因係因為用得返依家啲鏡"},{"pid":"8992a03f0f802f6d6280a5c96a0b3d5f8f082d6b","tid":100921,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講無錯，但你影相唔會咁影嘛<br />\n正確黎講係咁<br />\n當apsc同ff都用一個視角影相 (eg 45 度標準人類視角)<br />\nff係淺景深過apsc<br />\n詳情睇下呢條片既中段，雖然係支那片，但幾實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5TwIlzNaco&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fd954916\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5TwIlzNaco</a></blockquote><br />\n我以前都以為片幅影響景深，點解有呢個講法，只不過係因為要做到相同視角，APSC用23，FF要用35，咁FF張相景深咪淺啲，因為焦距長左。<span style=\"color: red;\">所以影響景深既最後都係得焦距同光圈</span>。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n仲有拍攝距離呢....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n攝距影響景深個效果仲大過焦距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9120803cb67ff7cdf62fcfea608c4b2665f27d8d","tid":100921,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>片幅唔會影響景深喎<br />\n<br />\n同一支鏡，企係同一位置<br />\n<br />\nFF 用apsc mode crop 返，同用apsc 機影出來係一樣架喎<br />\n<br />\n景深唔同係因為拎apsc 機行近咗去追返俾crop 嘅部份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打唔識唔好扮識wor,景深同pixel density同放大比率都有關係<br />\n<br />\nbtw FF最大優勢係DR大同解放舊鏡,景深呢d野我唔多care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npixel density同景深有咩關係?</blockquote><br />\n計DoF 有個factor叫CoC,呢樣野同出相放大率有關係<br />\n<br />\n就當你出24寸mon睇相,兩者都係用1080 resolution,如果相像素&gt;screen resolution,其實兩者係無分別的<br />\n<br />\n但如果你出到去牆身poster咁大張的相,如果FF行crop mode下像素密度同APSC像素密度唔同, d &quot;pixel&quot;會影響到最終輸出解像力,呢樣野要計埋你企係幾遠距離睇<br />\n<br />\n舊時菲林放大機年代呢d野有套formula去計,8R 最佳距離係30cm左右,呢樣係CoC公式入面有計到,仲關乎人眼resolution先決定到最終的&quot;景深&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而景深同散景,又係兩樣好相近但係唔相同的concept來的,景深淺但係散景會化d,但兩支鏡景深一樣唔代表一樣咁化的"},{"pid":"6e913a647d93f4872a4046116a61c24ec83bf71a","tid":100921,"uid":50056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我以前都以為片幅影響景深，點解有呢個講法，只不過係因為要做到相同視角，APSC用23，FF要用35，咁FF張相景深咪淺啲，因為焦距長左。<span style=\"color: red;\">所以影響景深既最後都係得焦距同光圈</span>。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n仲有拍攝距離呢....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n攝距影響景深個效果仲大過焦距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n漏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc8bd66d70230c501c34789cd41419d999e5622","tid":100921,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"好撚柒煩<br />\n又講景深同片幅<br />\n<br />\n依家又唔係係度研究影響景深既factors<br />\n總之FF同APSC同一framing視角下景深會淺左啦"},{"pid":"a9730f5b9354a728ffc8ed1133b813e3cb458b8c","tid":100921,"uid":52040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a6000轉a7ii  最大分別係用老鏡 其他冇咩應覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺唔覺夜景高iso手持表現好左好多？"},{"pid":"e0ad781218719313dcbc8120e83ec8ac51e7a151","tid":100921,"uid":77644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"其實最大分別真係DR FF影完RAW 出黎 <br />\n就算番到屋企發現曝光錯左都好 <br />\n係LR 到要救相 OR 想POST PROCESSING <br />\nFF 出黎既RAW 檔都可易輕易幫到你"},{"pid":"afcaca2fa465b559d5d2465959cbbf53e205051a","tid":100921,"uid":52040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由Sony a5100跟住去轉左ff一年半<br />\n依家轉番XT1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁玩？<br />\n像素唔是低左咩？"},{"pid":"1d76e15a954eb9dd1547fc41ca6363e631cecee3","tid":100921,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>a6000轉a7ii  最大分別係用老鏡 其他冇咩應覺<